Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.49,0:00:11.36,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.86,0:00:13.95,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,枕頭變了我睡不著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.28,0:00:15.91,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,也是有這樣子的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.16,0:00:18.53,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,平時我都會從家裡把枕頭帶過來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.79,0:00:19.24,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,特地帶過來？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.87,0:00:23.50,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們來為了讓你能睡得香提供點幫助吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.58,0:00:25.83,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.25,0:00:30.38,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我們三個被稱為「低音安眠三巨頭」的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:31.92,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,才沒被這麼叫啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.13,0:00:33.88,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,這東西我也算在裡面的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.34,0:00:35.51,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這樣葉月醬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.76,0:00:38.72,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,請務必傳授麗奈醬點能入睡的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.97,0:00:39.68,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.89,0:00:40.60,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.93,0:00:44.14,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 說到入睡的方法也就只有一個啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.06,0:00:46.10,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那說白了就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.56,0:00:47.40,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,就是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.52,0:00:49.73,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,想睡的話隨時都能睡著
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.73,0:00:53.03,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,靠氣勢啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.78,0:00:54.70,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,睡著了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.70,0:00:56.03,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是葉月醬
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.57,0:00:57.53,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,真厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.20,0:01:00.58,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來由我來教你我秘藏的絕招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.08,0:01:03.54,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,麗奈醬首先把眼睛閉上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:08.21,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,然後 正常的話應該是數羊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.63,0:01:11.42,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不過我的話是數喜歡的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.01,0:01:13.13,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.88,0:01:16.26,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,一個瀧老師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.72,0:01:18.09,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,兩個瀧老師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.76,0:01:20.10,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,三個瀧老師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.06,0:01:22.60,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,和瀧老師野餐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.52,0:01:24.85,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,和瀧老師度假
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.44,0:01:27.48,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,和瀧老師在海邊追逐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.50,0:01:30.36,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,和瀧老師結婚…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.82,0:01:34.78,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,和大號君的甜蜜婚禮…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.86,0:01:37.32,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,麗奈你還睡不著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.82,0:01:39.41,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 有點興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.87,0:01:40.41,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,興奮？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.91,0:01:43.12,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子知不知道什麼能入睡的好方法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:46.04,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我？ 沒有喔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:47.37,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.96,0:01:49.33,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼「果然」啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.96,0:01:53.84,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不過小時候媽媽會給我讀連環畫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.05,0:01:54.84,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,連環畫？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.42,0:01:57.38,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來我也有被讀過
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.01,0:01:58.68,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼樣的？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:03.31,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,很久很久以前 某個地方有一個老爺爺和一個老婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.93,0:02:06.52,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,老婆婆在河邊洗衣服的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:08.39,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,河上飄過來一個很大的桃子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:11.90,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,從撿來的桃子裡誕生出一個活潑的嬰兒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.36,0:02:13.98,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,他們給他取名叫做桃太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.48,0:02:18.36,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,然後有一天 為了去退治鬼的桃太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.82,0:02:21.37,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,和狗 猴子 雉雞一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:24.29,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛 就是「桃太郎」來著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:25.87,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,久美子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.50,0:02:33.21,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,咋回事啊 這個
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:41.91,Hibike zw,NTP,0,0,0,,完
